law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 226, sec. 113, effective July 15, 1998; amended ch. 488, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1998. -- Created 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 225, sec. 6, effective June 17, 1978.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/98). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 226 prevails over its amendment in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 488.
